US rapper The Game real name Jayceon Terrell Taylor will have to pay $7.13 million just over a R100 million to Priscilla Rainey. According to TMZ, Rainey sued The Game for allegedly sexually assaulting her while shooting a reality show for VH1 She s Got Game in 2015. She claimed the rapper allegedly forced his hand inside her dress to rub her bare genitalia and buttocks, during the shooting of the video. The rapper&#8217;s team denied the claims. Rainey filed a lawsuit against The Game for $10 million in August of 2015, an Illinois court ruled in favour of Rainey, finding Game guilty but did not granting the full amount that was requested by Rainey. Meanwhile it has been reported that the rapper plans to appeal the ruling. -TNA Reporter//